          <h1 id="about">About MEG</h1>
          <p class="lead">MEG combines elements of distributed and PKI infrastructures to solve many of the problems with current email encryption options.</p>
          <h2>MEG is</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Best effort - it will encrypt when it can, but won't prevent you from communicating</li>
            <li>Transparent - It will give you as much information as you want about what its doing and will prompt a user before making any insecure choices</li>
            <li>Federated - A company can control keys like PKI but can interact securely with individuals who want to stay unassociated</li>
          </ul>

